To Run Application You have to 

1) Install WxPython 
	sudo apt-get install python-wxversion spe
2)Running Application:
	python TweetOnDesktop.py
3)Configuring Account
	settings -> Configure Account -> Give Your Consumer Key, Consumer Secret,Account Key, Account Secret
	the above four credentials are called OAuth Authentication credentials . If You have no OAuth credentials 
	You can go to 
			https://dev.twitter.com/apps/1469082/show
	and register and get above credentials 
4) Now things are as simple , 
	Enter Your tweet and click Tweet To Tweet
	click fetch Tweets To See Yours Friends Tweets .......
 

